%% Data Sources
A[hacker_news.comments] %% Comments data from the Hacker News dataset

%% BigQuery Client Setup
B[client] %% BigQuery Client object
C[dataset_ref] %% Reference to Dataset
D[table_ref] %% Reference to Table
E[table] %% Fetched comments Table

%% Queries and Analysis
F[prolific_commenters_query] %% SQL for prolific commenters
G[deleted_posts_query] %% SQL for counting deleted posts

%% DataFrames
H[prolific_commenters] %% DataFrame of authors with >10k posts
I[deleted_posts] %% DataFrame of deleted post count

%% Data Source to Client
A -->|Fetched by| B

%% Client to Dataset and Table References
B -->|Creates| C
C -->|Creates| D
D -->|Fetches| E

%% Table to Queries
E -->|Runs SQL to fetch| F
E -->|Runs SQL to fetch| G

%% Queries to DataFrames
F -->|Executes and stores in| H
G -->|Executes and stores in| I

%% Output Flow
H -->|Displayed in notebook| O1[output/display]
I -->|Displayed in notebook| O2[output/display]
